{"name":"Striker","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-gray.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>Prerequisite: 4th level</em></p>\n<p>You master a never ending series of movements and attacks.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase trength, Dexterity or Constitution by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>Immediately before or after making a weapon attack with a melee weapon, you can move 5 feet without provoking attacks of opportunity.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Grants: @Item[y1k3iiGdU4bL69TD]{Flowing Strikes}</p>\n<h2>Flowing Strikes</h2>\n<p><em>Active Ability (Action)</em></p>\n<p>As an action, you can move up to 15 feet. Each time you move into range of a new creature, you can make one melee weapon attack against the creature. This can only hit a creature once per turn, and each time you move you can only attack once (even if moving into reach of multiple new creatures). You can make a maximum number of attacks this way equal to your proficiency bonus. If you are wielding two weapons with the Light property, you can use your bonus action to make one additional attack in this way.</p>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you complete a short or long rest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Kibbles' Active Martial Feats","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Level 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZltBRX3qCs8ZDdsL":3},"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickDesc":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickOther":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true,"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.XJDUARAtJCnABZ5R"}},"_id":"49by1kBwZCJgqeSw"}
{"name":"Body Guard: Heroic Intervention","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/shield-block-bash-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a reaction, when an allied creature within 30 feet of you takes damage, you can move up to your movement speed to them. You move into their space, and they move to an unoccupied space of their choice within 5 feet, or the closest unoccupied space if there are no unoccupied spaces within 5 feet. You and the target creature have resistance to all damage until the start of your next turn.</p>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you complete a short or long rest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Body Guard Feat","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Body Guard Feat","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZltBRX3qCs8ZDdsL":3},"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickDesc":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickOther":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickCharges":{"value":{"use":true},"altValue":{"use":true}}},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.DGYC5R2ykXaH1wX8"}},"_id":"4gvqAc1y6WC900K2"}
{"name":"Grappler","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist-yellow-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>Prerequisite: 4th level</em></p>\n<p>Your master grappling and leverage to pin and fling your foes.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase your Strength or Constitution by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>You have advantage on attack rolls against a creature you are grappling.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Grants: @Item[rCvciOForvmwO73P]{Martial Toss}</p>\n<h2>Martial Toss</h2>\n<p><em>Active Ability (Action)</em></p>\n<p>As a action, you attempt to lift a creature or object your size or smaller within reach. The target must make a Strength saving throw. An object or creature you are grappling automatically fails. If you successfully lift them, you can move 5 feet in direction and throw them an additional 15 feet in the direction moved as part of the same action.</p>\n<p>The creatures movement ends early if it collides with another creature or obstacle. The creature and anything it collides with takes 2d8 + your Strength modifier and falls prone unless it one or more sizes larger than the thrown creature. The number of d8 increases by one when your proficiency bonus increases (with the total number of d8 equaling your proficiency bonus).</p>\n<p>After throwing the object or creature, you can make one weapon attack or grapple as a bonus action before the end of your turn.</p>\n<p>Once you use this feature to successful throw a creature or object, you cannot use it again until you complete a short or long rest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Kibbles' Active Martial Feats","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Level 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZltBRX3qCs8ZDdsL":3},"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickDesc":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickOther":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true,"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.eRdAhrCu1JvY8jFf"}},"_id":"Aqc0tLq2UBwyazsn"}
{"name":"Brute: Brutal Takedown","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/wounds/injury-pain-body-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a reaction to reducing a creature to 0 hit points, you can perform a brutal display that forces all hostile creatures of the same creature type within 60 feet that can see or hear you to make a Wisdom shaving throw, or become frightened of you until the start of your next turn.</p>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you complete a short or long rest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Brute Feat","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Brute Feat","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZltBRX3qCs8ZDdsL":3},"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickDesc":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickOther":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true,"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9JqO3pFr4AOqGD10"}},"_id":"ChVBIMmUvuC4SY5C"}
{"name":"Dagger Expert","type":"feat","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-twin-curved-black.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You are a well versed expert on daggers, able to use them fluidly any situation.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You can draw or stow and number of daggers during your turn. You have advantage on any check to conceal your daggers.</li>\n<li>Your attacks with daggers score a critical hit on a roll of 19 or 20.</li>\n<li>When you use two-weapon fighting using a dagger in both hands, your can take both attacks as part of the Attack action on your turn (without expending your bonus action). You can only make this attack once per turn.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Kibbles' Generic Feats","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"HHdSeBhWJxwazlVB","changes":[{"key":"flags.dnd5e.weaponCriticalThreshold","mode":5,"value":"19","priority":50}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-twin-curved-black.webp","label":"Dagger Expert","origin":"Item.YjTAGwp1WJPZXdIa","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZltBRX3qCs8ZDdsL":3},"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickDesc":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickOther":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true,"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.YjTAGwp1WJPZXdIa"}},"_id":"DWgg3RJwFScpMRtu"}
